<Layout title="Depreciation Clawback When Selling a Brisbane Investment Property 2026 | Daniel Gierach Property" description="When you sell a Brisbane investment property, depreciation claimed on fixtures and fittings can trigger a tax obligation you did not budget for. Here is how it works and what to do about it." schema={faqSchema}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
